data.description: Contract pending - on the market for back up offers only. 4 bed 5 bath Papillion 2-story situated on an oversized 0.37 acre lot in popular Shadow Lake! Bright & airy 2-story entry w/a curved staircase. Gorgeous hardwood floors throughout main level living areas w/a formal dining rm, spacious living rm offering a cozy fireplace nestled within custom built-ins & fantastic kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances (double ovens!), granite countertops, walk-in pantry & great eating area surrounded by windows. Lrg main level laundry & great drop zone w/built-ins. Upstairs, you'll find a sizable primary suite complete w/a fireplace & full bath w/a jetted tub. Three secondary bedrms all w/direct access to bathrms. Finished lower level boasting an expansive family rm/rec rm, 3/4 bath & two flex rms great for non-conforming bedrms, office, exercise rm, or playrm! Outside, enjoy the expanded patio & gazebo overlooking a fully fenced flat yard & miles of neighborhood trails & lakes! AMA
